title: Glee: The Ultimate Third Season
description:
The complete third season of Glee, with all 22 episodes, with the never-before-seen (because I edited it myself) extended versions of "Extraordinary Merry Christmas" (season 3, episode 9) and "Michael" (season 3, episode 11).

1. The Purple Piano Project
2. I Am Unicorn
3. Asian F
4. Pot O' Gold
5. The First Time
6. Mash Off
7. I Kissed a Girl
8. Hold on to Sixteen
9. Extraordinary Merry Christmas
10. Yes/No
11. Michael
12. The Spanish Teacher
13. Heart
14. On My Way
15. Big Brother
16. Saturday Night Glee-ver
17. Dance with Somebody
18. Choke
19. Prom-asaurus
20. Props
21. Nationals
22. Goodbye

This package also includes the CDs released throughout season 3, including Volumes 7, The Christmas Album Volume 2, and The Graduation Album.

Eight deleted scenes are also featured:
1. Oklahoma! (from "Mash Off")
2. Santana comes out (from "I Kissed a Girl")
3. Santa Baby (from "Extraordinary Merry Christmas")
4. Klaine box scene (from "Extraordinary Merry Christmas")
5. I Want You Back (from "Michael")
6. Bridesmaids (from "On My Way")
7. Rachel's yearbook message to Kurt (from "Goodbye")
8. Mike's gift from his parents (from "Goodbye")

As an added bonus, in separate episode folders, I have included the original versions of the songs featured on Glee. This is something I do myself.
